{"tid":450030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國及歐盟 : 支 持 西班牙 維 護 統 一","createTime":"2017-10-27T18:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T01:11:07.000Z","uid":62257,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"db1d0fa7dc9363f79a2e02f57d5be94d5849dab5","tid":450030,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=973237&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D973237%26csid%3D261_367&d=09TkYiiD4Im0BfhqrAO4sdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3cca7d1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=973237&amp;csid=261_367</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n����ӥx�A�ȱ����K�d�n���p���F���s�i�A���p���ڭ�FAQ���v�[�J�ڭ�會員登記<br />\n<br />\n即時新聞 | 國際<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;即時新聞&nbsp;--- 本地及兩岸&nbsp;--- 國際&nbsp;--- 財經&nbsp;--- 體育&nbsp;--- 立法會道一號&nbsp;交通消息&nbsp;--- 即時交通&nbsp;--- 特別封路&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n美國及歐盟支持西班牙維護統一<br />\n<br />\n27.10.2017 23:34<br />\n<br />\n美國及歐盟都支持西班牙維護統一的立場；美國國務院強調，加泰羅尼亞是西班牙一部份，美方支持西班牙政府致力維持國家強大及統一，又指西班牙是美國在北約的盟友，雙方會在安全及經濟事宜，緊密合作。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲理事會主席圖斯克指，加泰羅尼亞宣布獨立不會有任何變化，歐盟只會與西班牙中央政府交往，但期望西班牙當局尋求對話，化解今次分裂危機，不要訴諸武力。"},{"pid":"43fb8020ef7130ebdbb8f1cb9bd8adfa21c08207","tid":450030,"uid":35815,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08ce73a82580b9e85da710c9edce70930d25b943","tid":450030,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T21:40:10.000Z","msg":"加州獨立啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa40d569e1af381ce84911ce6d7e696ac039d32","tid":450030,"uid":72638,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T21:41:37.000Z","msg":"連登小朋友們被打臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\